These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, rose, lily, iris
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Flower   | poppy | rose | daffodil | iris | lily |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, november, march, january, july
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Birthday   | march  | january   | december       | november    | july   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, iced-tea, water, 7up
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Beverage        | iced-tea | water | cola | tea | 7up |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, bellflower, daffodil, begonia
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Flower   | daffodil    | rose        | bellflower | poppy | begonia |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

