.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, august, november, april, february
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, swimming, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Birthday    | november   | september     | august   | april         | february |
| Sport   | biathlon | volleyball | swimming | weightlifting | rowing     |

