.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
5 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, go, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the person playing go##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Game       | mah-jongg   | go   | snooker | backgammon | scrabble |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike | roller   | skateboard | car       |

