.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, february, june, august, october
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Birthday   | august | june | february | december   | october |

