.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, engineer, manager, scientist, teacher
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, photography, fishing, traveling, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | engineer | chef       | teacher | scientist | manager    |
| Hobby   | traveling   | sudoku | fishing  | photography     | writing |

