.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, biathlon, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | photography | camping | magic-tricks | woodworking | dancing |
| Sport   | biathlon       | swimming   | weightlifting         | snowboarding   | rowing   |

