.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, firefighter, manager, dressmaker
5 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, rat
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the firefighter##1
3. the owner of the frog is the security-guard##1
4. the manager is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Job   | dressmaker | manager | nurse | firefighter | security-guard |
| Pet           | rat      | fish    | goldfish  | dog     | frog     |

