.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: apple, artichoke, avocado, cherry, pomegranate
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, lilac, turquise, white, emerald
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes lilac is the person eating cherry##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who likes red##1
7. the person who likes emerald is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | cherry | apple  | avocado | artichoke | pomegranate |
| Color    | lilac    | white | emerald   | red       | turquise        |

