.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, german, mexican, spanish
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, action, fantasy, romance
1. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the dutch##1
4. the spanish is the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the mexican is in the middle##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | german | dutch      | mexican | egyptian | spanish |
| Movie-Genre     | fantasy  | mystery | documentary     | romance     | action  |

