4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating corn##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Food      | broccoli | kiwi | corn      | raspberry | pomegranate      |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican       | argentine | turkish  | indonesian |

