3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the indian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
6. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the thai is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday           | december     | november | february | june  | august |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai               | french     | indian | nigerian |

