.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-16::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, blueberry, lime, peach
5 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, cat, frog, guinea-pig
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
3. the person eating apricot is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Food    | asparagus   | blueberry | peach      | apricot | lime        |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | mouse     | cat | goldfish | frog |

