.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, gospel, hip-hop, house, rock
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, 7up, cola, juice
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of blues is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
6. the fan of house is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | hip-hop    | rock | house   | gospel |
| Beverage     | lemonade | hot-chocolate | cola | 7up | juice    |

