.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, papaya, cucumber, lime, pumpkin
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, rugby, swimming
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person eating peas is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Food   | papaya   | lime  | peas | pumpkin | cucumber  |
| Sport         | badminton | cricket | rugby  | swimming    | baseball |

