.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, hedgehog, goldfish, ferret
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, handball, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Pet   | ferret     | hedgehog       | mouse     | guinea-pig  | goldfish  |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | cricket | tennis | handball |

