.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, satire, thriller
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, argentine, brazilian, spanish
1. the chinese is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the spanish##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | romance | documentary | satire |
| Nationality           | spanish | brazilian  | chinese    | indonesian  | argentine   |

 